  <span>⭐ Important Exam Notes — All Units</span>
</div>

<div class="imp-banner">
  <div class="imp-banner-icon">📌</div>
  <div class="imp-banner-text">
    <h3>Important Exam Notes — Units 1 to 8</h3>
    <p>Concise exam-ready points with diagrams, memory tricks, and model answers for every unit.</p>
  </div>
