<!-- ─── IMP UNIT 1 ─── -->
<div class="imp-unit-card">
  <div class="imp-unit-header bg-u1" onclick="toggleImp(this)">
    <span class="imp-unit-badge">UNIT 1</span>
    <span style="font-size:1.5rem">🌿</span>
    <h3>Human–Environment Interaction, City States, Industrial Revolution &amp; Ethics</h3>
    <button class="toggle-btn">▼</button>
  </div>
  <div class="imp-unit-body">

    <!-- Topic 1 -->
    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u1">🔁 1. Man and Environment Interaction</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Humans depend on the environment for food, water, shelter, and resources. At the same time, human activities affect the environment in positive and negative ways.</p>
        <div class="pos-neg-grid">
          <div class="pos-card">
            <h5>✅ Positive Interactions</h5>
            <ul><li>🌲 Tree plantation</li><li>🦁 Wildlife conservation</li><li>☀️ Renewable energy use</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="neg-card">
            <h5>❌ Negative Interactions</h5>
            <ul><li>🪓 Deforestation</li><li>☁️ Pollution</li><li>📉 Overuse of resources</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="imp-flow" style="margin-top:14px">
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u1">🌍 Environment</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓ Provides Resources</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#27ae60">👤 Humans</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓ Use &amp; Modify</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u4">⚡ Modified Environment</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Topic 2 -->
    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u1">🏛️ 2. Emergence of City States</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Early human settlements gradually developed into organized cities and states as agriculture improved and populations grew.</p>
        <div class="info-grid" style="margin-top:10px">
          <div class="info-card light-u1"><span class="ic-icon">🏺</span><div class="ic-label">Indus Valley</div><div class="ic-sub">One of earliest urban civilizations</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u1"><span class="ic-icon">🏛️</span><div class="ic-label">Mesopotamia</div><div class="ic-sub">Between Tigris &amp; Euphrates rivers</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u1"><span class="ic-icon">🔺</span><div class="ic-label">Egyptian</div><div class="ic-sub">Nile River civilization</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="tag-list" style="margin-top:10px">
          <span class="tag bg-u1">🤝 Better Trade</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u1">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Population Growth</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u4">📦 Increased Resource Use</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Topic 3 -->
    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u1">🏭 3. Industrial Revolution and Its Impact</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Started in <strong>England in the 18th century</strong> when machines replaced manual labour.</p>
        <div class="pos-neg-grid">
          <div class="pos-card">
            <h5>✅ Positive Impacts</h5>
            <ul><li>📈 Increased production</li><li>🚂 Better transportation</li><li>💰 Economic growth</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="neg-card">
            <h5>❌ Negative Impacts</h5>
            <ul><li>💨 Air pollution</li><li>💧 Water pollution</li><li>⛏️ Resource depletion</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="imp-flow" style="margin-top:14px">
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u4">🏭 Industrial Revolution</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#e67e22">⚙️ Factories &amp; Machines</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#f39c12">📦 More Production</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u4">☁️ More Pollution</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Topic 4 -->
    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u1">🌿 4. Environmental Ethics</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Moral principles guiding human behavior towards nature. It says we have a responsibility to protect the natural world.</p>
        <div class="tag-list">
          <span class="tag bg-u1">🤝 Respect Nature</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u1">🦁 Protect Wildlife</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u1">♻️ Use Resources Responsibly</span>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#eafaf1;border-color:var(--u1);margin-top:12px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u1">🧠 Example</div>
          <div class="mb-content">Saving forests for future generations is an act of environmental ethics.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Topic 5 -->
    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u1">🌐 5. Stockholm Conference (1972)</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="effect-row">
          <div class="effect-card light-u1"><span class="ec-icon">🏆</span><div class="ec-title text-u1">First Major Environmental Conference</div><ul><li>Organized by the United Nations</li><li>Raised global environmental awareness</li><li>Established UNEP (UN Environment Programme)</li></ul></div>
          <div class="effect-card light-u2"><span class="ec-icon">📜</span><div class="ec-title text-u2">Key Outcomes</div><ul><li>Declaration on Human Environment</li><li>Action Plan for Environment</li><li>Start of global environmental governance</li></ul></div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#eaf4fb;border-color:var(--u2);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u2">🧠 Memory Trick</div>
          <div class="mb-content">Stockholm (1972) = START of Global Environmental Action 🌱</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Topic 6 -->
    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u1">📋 6. Brundtland Commission (1987)</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p><strong>Official Name:</strong> World Commission on Environment and Development.</p>
        <div class="formula-box">
          <div style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:6px">Famous Definition of Sustainable Development</div>
          <div class="formula-text" style="font-size:1rem">"Meeting present needs without compromising future generations' ability to meet their needs."</div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#eafaf1;border-color:var(--u1)">
          <div class="mb-title text-u1">🧠 Key Fact</div>
          <div class="mb-content">Brundtland Commission = Introduced the concept of Sustainable Development globally</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Topic 7 -->
    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u1">🌎 7. Rio Summit (1992) — Earth Summit</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Held at <strong>Rio de Janeiro, Brazil.</strong> Also called the Earth Summit.</p>
        <div class="info-grid" style="margin-top:10px">
          <div class="info-card light-u1"><span class="ic-icon">📋</span><div class="ic-label">Agenda 21</div><div class="ic-sub">Global action plan for sustainable development</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u6"><span class="ic-icon">🌡️</span><div class="ic-label">Climate Convention</div><div class="ic-sub">Framework on Climate Change (UNFCCC)</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u3"><span class="ic-icon">🌿</span><div class="ic-label">CBD</div><div class="ic-sub">Convention on Biological Diversity</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="imp-flow" style="margin-top:12px">
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u1">🌎 Rio Summit 1992</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#27ae60">♻️ Sustainable Development Promoted</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u2">🤝 Global Cooperation Begun</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="qr-strip">
      <h4>⚡ Unit 1 Quick Revision</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>🌍 Environment = Biotic + Abiotic components</li>
        <li>🔁 Human–Env Interaction = Positive &amp; Negative</li>
        <li>🏛️ City States → Indus Valley, Mesopotamia, Egypt</li>
        <li>🏭 Industrial Revolution (18th Century England) = More Production + More Pollution</li>
        <li>🌿 Environmental Ethics = Moral duty to protect nature</li>
        <li>🌐 Stockholm 1972 = First major global environment conference</li>
        <li>📋 Brundtland 1987 = Defined Sustainable Development</li>
        <li>🌎 Rio Summit 1992 = Agenda 21 + Climate Convention + CBD</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ─── IMP UNIT 2 ─── -->
<div class="imp-unit-card">
  <div class="imp-unit-header bg-u2" onclick="toggleImp(this)">
    <span class="imp-unit-badge">UNIT 2</span>
    <span style="font-size:1.5rem">💧</span>
    <h3>Energy Resources, SDGs, Water Scarcity &amp; Mineral Exploitation</h3>
    <button class="toggle-btn">▼</button>
  </div>
  <div class="imp-unit-body">

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u2">⚡ 1. Energy Resources — Renewable vs Non-Renewable</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <table class="styled-table">
          <thead><tr><th class="bg-u2">Feature</th><th class="bg-u2">Renewable ♻️</th><th class="bg-u2">Non-Renewable ⛏️</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Quantity</td><td>Unlimited</td><td>Limited</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Environmental Impact</td><td>Eco-friendly ✅</td><td>Polluting ❌</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Future Use</td><td>Sustainable</td><td>Exhaustible</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Examples</td><td>Solar, Wind, Hydro, Biomass</td><td>Coal, Petroleum, Natural Gas</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u2">🎯 2. SDGs — Sustainable Development Goals</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p><strong>17 Goals adopted by the UN in 2015</strong> as part of the 2030 Agenda for Sustainable Development.</p>
        <div class="circular-badges">
          <div class="c-badge" style="background:#00aed9"><span class="cb-icon">💧</span>Clean Water SDG 6</div>
          <div class="c-badge" style="background:#fcc30b;color:#333"><span class="cb-icon">⚡</span>Clean Energy SDG 7</div>
          <div class="c-badge" style="background:#3f7e44"><span class="cb-icon">🌡️</span>Climate Action SDG 13</div>
          <div class="c-badge" style="background:#0a97d9"><span class="cb-icon">🐠</span>Below Water SDG 14</div>
          <div class="c-badge" style="background:#56c02b"><span class="cb-icon">🌿</span>Life on Land SDG 15</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u2">💧 3. Water Scarcity and Water Conflicts</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="effect-row">
          <div class="effect-card light-u2"><span class="ec-icon">😟</span><div class="ec-title text-u2">Causes of Water Scarcity</div><ul><li>👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Population growth</li><li>☁️ Climate change</li><li>💧 Pollution of water bodies</li><li>📉 Overuse of groundwater</li></ul></div>
          <div class="effect-card light-u4"><span class="ec-icon">⚔️</span><div class="ec-title text-u4">Water Conflicts</div><ul><li>Disputes over water resources</li><li>Between states/countries</li><li>Example: Cauvery River dispute (Karnataka vs Tamil Nadu)</li></ul></div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#eaf4fb;border-color:var(--u2);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u2">🧠 Key Fact</div>
          <div class="mb-content">Cauvery River Dispute = Classic example of inter-state water conflict in India 🇮🇳</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u2">⛏️ 4. Mineral Exploitation and Harmful Effects</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Extraction of minerals from the Earth for industrial use.</p>
        <div class="pos-neg-grid">
          <div class="pos-card">
            <h5>✅ Advantages</h5>
            <ul><li>🏗️ Industrial development</li><li>👷 Employment generation</li><li>💰 Economic growth</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="neg-card">
            <h5>❌ Harmful Effects</h5>
            <ul><li>🌲 Deforestation</li><li>🏔️ Land degradation</li><li>💧 Water pollution</li><li>🦋 Habitat destruction</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#eaf4fb;border-color:var(--u2);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u2">🧠 Example</div>
          <div class="mb-content">Open-cast coal mining destroys large areas of land and forests. 🪨</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="qr-strip">
      <h4>⚡ Unit 2 Quick Revision</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>☀️ Renewable = Unlimited &amp; Eco-friendly | ⛏️ Non-Renewable = Limited &amp; Polluting</li>
        <li>🎯 17 SDGs adopted by UN in 2015</li>
        <li>💧 Water Scarcity = Lack of clean water due to pollution &amp; overuse</li>
        <li>⚔️ Cauvery Dispute = Example of water conflict</li>
        <li>⛏️ Mining = Development + Destruction</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ─── IMP UNIT 3 ─── -->
<div class="imp-unit-card">
  <div class="imp-unit-header bg-u3" onclick="toggleImp(this)">
    <span class="imp-unit-badge">UNIT 3</span>
    <span style="font-size:1.5rem">🌳</span>
    <h3>Ozone Depletion, Disasters, Acid Rain, Land Degradation &amp; Afforestation</h3>
    <button class="toggle-btn">▼</button>
  </div>
  <div class="imp-unit-body">

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u3">🌀 1. Ozone Layer Depletion</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Thinning of the ozone layer in the stratosphere. Main cause: <strong>CFCs (Chlorofluorocarbons)</strong> used in refrigerators and aerosols.</p>
        <div class="imp-flow">
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#f39c12">☀️ Sun UV Rays</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u3">🌀 Ozone Layer (Normal Protection)</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u1">🌍 Earth — Protected</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;margin:8px 0;font-weight:700;color:var(--u4)">⬇ When Ozone Depletes:</div>
        <div class="imp-flow">
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u4">⚠️ More UV Rays Reach Earth</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#c0392b">🤒 Skin Cancer + Eye Cataracts + Crop Damage</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tag-list" style="margin-top:10px">
          <span class="tag bg-u4">🔬 Skin Cancer</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u4">👁️ Eye Cataracts</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u4">🌿 Plant Damage</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u3">🛡️ Solution: Montreal Protocol (1987)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u3">🌪️ 2. Natural Disasters</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card light-u3"><span class="ic-icon">🌊</span><div class="ic-label">Flood</div><div class="ic-sub">Heavy rainfall, river overflow</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u3"><span class="ic-icon">🏚️</span><div class="ic-label">Earthquake</div><div class="ic-sub">Tectonic plate movement</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u3"><span class="ic-icon">🌋</span><div class="ic-label">Volcano</div><div class="ic-sub">Magma eruption</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u3"><span class="ic-icon">🌀</span><div class="ic-label">Cyclone</div><div class="ic-sub">Tropical storms</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u3"><span class="ic-icon">🌊</span><div class="ic-label">Tsunami</div><div class="ic-sub">Underwater earthquakes</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="tag-list" style="margin-top:10px">
          <span class="tag bg-u4">💀 Loss of Life</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u4">🏚️ Property Damage</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u4">🌍 Environmental Destruction</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u3">🌧️ 3. Acid Rain</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Caused by <strong>SO₂ + NOx</strong> emissions from industries reacting with water vapor in clouds.</p>
        <div class="imp-flow">
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#e74c3c">🏭 SO₂ + NOx from Industries</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓ Reacts with water in clouds</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#c0392b">💧 Sulfuric &amp; Nitric Acid Formed</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u4">🌧️ Acid Rain Falls</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tag-list" style="margin-top:10px">
          <span class="tag bg-u4">🏛️ Damages Monuments (Taj Mahal)</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u4">🌾 Harms Crops</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u4">🐟 Acidifies Lakes</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u3">🌫️ 4. Smog</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="formula-box">
          <div class="formula-text">💨 Smoke + 🌫️ Fog = 😶‍🌫️ SMOG</div>
        </div>
        <p>Caused by vehicle and industrial emissions.</p>
        <div class="tag-list">
          <span class="tag bg-u3">🫁 Breathing Problems</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u3">👁️ Reduced Visibility</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u3">🤒 Respiratory Diseases</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u3">🏔️ 5. Land Degradation &amp; Deforestation</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="compare-row">
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#fdf2f2;border-left:4px solid var(--u4)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u4)">🏔️ Land Degradation</h4>
            <ul><li>Overgrazing → Soil bare</li><li>Mining → Land destroyed</li><li>Deforestation → Erosion increases</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#fdf2f2;border-left:4px solid var(--u4)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u4)">🌲 Deforestation Effects</h4>
            <ul><li>🦋 Biodiversity loss</li><li>🏜️ Soil erosion</li><li>🌡️ Climate change</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u1">🌱 6. Afforestation</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Planting trees in barren or deforested land to restore green cover.</p>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card light-u1"><span class="ic-icon">💚</span><div class="ic-label">Increases Greenery</div><div class="ic-sub">Restores ecosystems</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u1"><span class="ic-icon">🏭</span><div class="ic-label">Reduces CO₂</div><div class="ic-sub">Acts as carbon sink</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u1"><span class="ic-icon">🏔️</span><div class="ic-label">Prevents Erosion</div><div class="ic-sub">Roots hold soil</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="qr-strip">
      <h4>⚡ Unit 3 Quick Revision</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>🌀 Ozone Depletion → CFC → More UV → Skin Cancer</li>
        <li>🌀 Montreal Protocol (1987) = Solution to Ozone Depletion</li>
        <li>🌧️ Acid Rain = SO₂ + NOx + Water → Sulfuric Acid</li>
        <li>😶‍🌫️ Smog = Smoke + Fog</li>
        <li>🌲 Deforestation → Biodiversity Loss + Soil Erosion + Climate Change</li>
        <li>🌱 Afforestation → Reduces CO₂ + Prevents Erosion</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ─── IMP UNIT 4 ─── -->
<div class="imp-unit-card">
  <div class="imp-unit-header bg-u4" onclick="toggleImp(this)">
    <span class="imp-unit-badge">UNIT 4</span>
    <span style="font-size:1.5rem">🦋</span>
    <h3>Biodiversity Hotspots, IUCN Categories, Ecosystem Services &amp; Threats</h3>
    <button class="toggle-btn">▼</button>
  </div>
  <div class="imp-unit-body">

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u4">🔥 1. Biodiversity Hotspots</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Regions with <strong>rich biodiversity</strong> but under significant threat of habitat loss.</p>
        <div class="compare-row">
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#fdf2f2;border-left:4px solid var(--u4)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u4)">📋 Conditions to be a Hotspot</h4>
            <ul><li>High number of endemic species</li><li>Significant habitat loss (70%+ lost)</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#eafaf1;border-left:4px solid var(--u1)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u1)">🇮🇳 Examples in India</h4>
            <ul><li>🌿 Western Ghats</li><li>🏔️ Himalayas</li><li>🏝️ Indo-Burma region</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u4">📊 2. IUCN Threat Categories</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>IUCN = <strong>International Union for Conservation of Nature</strong></p>
        <div class="iucn-ladder">
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#2ecc71;width:320px">✅ LC — Least Concern</div>
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#f1c40f;color:#333;width:280px;margin-top:4px">⚠️ NT — Near Threatened</div>
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#e67e22;width:240px;margin-top:4px">🔶 VU — Vulnerable</div>
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#e74c3c;width:200px;margin-top:4px">🔴 EN — Endangered</div>
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#c0392b;width:160px;margin-top:4px">🆘 CR — Critically Endangered</div>
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#7f8c8d;width:120px;margin-top:4px">💀 EX — Extinct</div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#fdf2f2;border-color:var(--u4);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u4">🧠 Example</div>
          <div class="mb-content">🐯 Tiger → Endangered (EN) &nbsp;|&nbsp; 🦅 Dodo → Extinct (EX)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u4">🌍 3. Ecosystem Services</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card light-u4"><span class="ic-icon">🍎</span><div class="ic-label">Provisioning</div><div class="ic-sub">Food, water, medicines</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u4"><span class="ic-icon">🌀</span><div class="ic-label">Regulating</div><div class="ic-sub">Climate, water purification, pollination</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u4"><span class="ic-icon">🔄</span><div class="ic-label">Supporting</div><div class="ic-sub">Nutrient cycling, soil formation</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u4"><span class="ic-icon">🎨</span><div class="ic-label">Cultural</div><div class="ic-sub">Recreation, tourism, spiritual value</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u4">⚠️ 4. Threats to Biodiversity — HIPPO</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="hippo-box">
          <h4>🦛 Remember: H-I-P-P-O</h4>
          <div class="hippo-row">
            <div class="hippo-item"><span class="hi-letter">H</span><div class="hi-word">Habitat Loss</div></div>
            <div class="hippo-item"><span class="hi-letter">I</span><div class="hi-word">Invasive Species</div></div>
            <div class="hippo-item"><span class="hi-letter">P</span><div class="hi-word">Pollution</div></div>
            <div class="hippo-item"><span class="hi-letter">P</span><div class="hi-word">Population Pressure</div></div>
            <div class="hippo-item"><span class="hi-letter">O</span><div class="hi-word">Overexploitation</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u4">🛡️ 5. Conservation — In-Situ vs Ex-Situ</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="compare-row">
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#eafaf1;border-left:4px solid var(--u1)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u1)">🏞️ In-Situ Conservation</h4>
            <p style="font-size:.82rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:8px">Protection in natural habitat.</p>
            <ul><li>🏕️ National Parks</li><li>🦁 Wildlife Sanctuaries</li><li>🌿 Biosphere Reserves</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#f5eef8;border-left:4px solid var(--u3)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u3)">🏛️ Ex-Situ Conservation</h4>
            <p style="font-size:.82rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:8px">Protection outside natural habitat.</p>
            <ul><li>🦓 Zoos</li><li>🌺 Botanical Gardens</li><li>🌱 Seed Banks</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="qr-strip">
      <h4>⚡ Unit 4 Quick Revision</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>🔥 Biodiversity Hotspot = Rich biodiversity + Under threat</li>
        <li>🇮🇳 India Hotspots = Western Ghats + Himalayas</li>
        <li>🐯 Tiger = Endangered | 💀 Dodo = Extinct</li>
        <li>🦛 HIPPO = 5 main threats to biodiversity</li>
        <li>🏞️ In-Situ = National Parks | 🏛️ Ex-Situ = Zoos, Seed Banks</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ─── IMP UNIT 5 ─── -->
<div class="imp-unit-card">
  <div class="imp-unit-header bg-u5" onclick="toggleImp(this)">
    <span class="imp-unit-badge">UNIT 5</span>
    <span style="font-size:1.5rem">☁️</span>
    <h3>All Types of Pollution — Complete Table</h3>
    <button class="toggle-btn">▼</button>
  </div>
  <div class="imp-unit-body">

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u5">🌫️ All 6 Types of Pollution</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card light-u4"><span class="ic-icon">💨</span><div class="ic-label">Air Pollution</div><div class="ic-sub">Vehicle smoke, industries, burning fuels</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u2"><span class="ic-icon">💧</span><div class="ic-label">Water Pollution</div><div class="ic-sub">Sewage, industrial waste, oil spills</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u7"><span class="ic-icon">🪨</span><div class="ic-label">Soil Pollution</div><div class="ic-sub">Pesticides, plastics, chemicals</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u5"><span class="ic-icon">📢</span><div class="ic-label">Noise Pollution</div><div class="ic-sub">Loudspeakers, traffic, machinery</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u4"><span class="ic-icon">🌡️</span><div class="ic-label">Thermal Pollution</div><div class="ic-sub">Hot water from factories/power plants</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u3"><span class="ic-icon">☢️</span><div class="ic-label">Radioactive Pollution</div><div class="ic-sub">Nuclear waste, accidents</div></div>
        </div>
        <table class="styled-table" style="margin-top:16px">
          <thead><tr><th class="bg-u5">Pollution Type</th><th class="bg-u5">Icon</th><th class="bg-u5">Main Source</th><th class="bg-u5">Key Effect</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td><b>Air</b></td><td>💨</td><td>Vehicle smoke</td><td>Asthma, Lung disease</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Water</b></td><td>💧</td><td>Sewage</td><td>Cholera, Typhoid</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Soil</b></td><td>🪨</td><td>Pesticides/Plastics</td><td>Reduced fertility</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Noise</b></td><td>📢</td><td>Traffic</td><td>Hearing loss, Stress</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Thermal</b></td><td>🌡️</td><td>Factories</td><td>Kills aquatic life</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Radioactive</b></td><td>☢️</td><td>Nuclear Plants</td><td>Cancer, Mutations</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="qr-strip">
      <h4>⚡ Unit 5 Quick Revision</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>💨 Air → Vehicle smoke → Asthma</li>
        <li>💧 Water → Sewage → Cholera</li>
        <li>🪨 Soil → Pesticides → Less fertility</li>
        <li>📢 Noise → Traffic → Hearing loss</li>
        <li>🌡️ Thermal → Hot water discharge → Aquatic death</li>
        <li>☢️ Radioactive → Nuclear waste → Cancer</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ─── IMP UNIT 6 ─── -->
<div class="imp-unit-card">
  <div class="imp-unit-header bg-u6" onclick="toggleImp(this)">
    <span class="imp-unit-badge">UNIT 6</span>
    <span style="font-size:1.5rem">🌡️</span>
    <h3>Climate Change Master Notes — 1.5°C Limit, Carbon Sink, Net Zero, Climate Justice &amp; NCAP</h3>
    <button class="toggle-btn">▼</button>
  </div>
  <div class="imp-unit-body">

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u6">🌡️ 1. Importance of 1.5°C and 2°C Temperature Limit</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Scientists believe that if global temperature rises above <strong>1.5°C–2°C</strong> compared to pre-industrial levels, climate impacts become very dangerous.</p>
        <div class="compare-row">
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#eafaf1;border-left:4px solid var(--u1)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u1)">✅ Below 1.5°C — Safer Future</h4>
            <ul><li>Less extreme weather</li><li>Protected coastal areas</li><li>Better food &amp; water security</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#fdf2f2;border-left:4px solid var(--u4)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u4)">❌ Above 2°C — Extreme Risks</h4>
            <ul><li>Severe heat waves</li><li>Melting glaciers + sea rise</li><li>Biodiversity collapse</li><li>Food &amp; water crises</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="exam-q-box">
          <div class="eq-label">🎯 Likely Exam Question</div>
          <div class="eq-q">Why is limiting global warming to 1.5°C important?</div>
          <div class="eq-a">Limiting warming to 1.5°C reduces extreme weather events, protects ecosystems, decreases sea-level rise, and improves food and water security for all nations.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u6">🌍 2. Global Warming</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p><strong>Definition:</strong> Gradual increase in Earth's average temperature due to accumulation of greenhouse gases.</p>
        <div class="imp-flow">
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u4">🏭 Fossil Fuel Burning</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#e67e22">📈 Increase in CO₂</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#c0392b">☁️ Enhanced Greenhouse Effect</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#8e44ad">🌡️ Global Warming</div>
        </div>
        <div class="effect-row" style="margin-top:12px">
          <div class="effect-card light-u4"><span class="ec-icon">🧊</span><div class="ec-title text-u4">Environmental</div><ul><li>Glacier melting</li><li>Heat waves</li><li>Floods &amp; Droughts</li></ul></div>
          <div class="effect-card light-u7"><span class="ec-icon">👤</span><div class="ec-title text-u7">Human Impact</div><ul><li>Food insecurity</li><li>Water shortage</li><li>Climate refugees</li></ul></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u6">🌿 3. Carbon Sink</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p><strong>Definition:</strong> Anything that absorbs more carbon dioxide than it releases.</p>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card light-u6"><span class="ic-icon">🌲</span><div class="ic-label">Forests</div><div class="ic-sub">Largest land carbon sink</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u6"><span class="ic-icon">🌊</span><div class="ic-label">Oceans</div><div class="ic-sub">Absorbs 30% of CO₂</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u6"><span class="ic-icon">🌿</span><div class="ic-label">Wetlands</div><div class="ic-sub">High carbon storage</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u6"><span class="ic-icon">🌴</span><div class="ic-label">Mangroves</div><div class="ic-sub">Coastal carbon storage</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="imp-flow" style="margin-top:12px">
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u4">☁️ CO₂ in Atmosphere</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓ Absorbed by</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u1">🌲 Forests / Oceans / Wetlands</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u6">✅ Carbon Stored — Climate Balanced</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u6">🎯 4. Net Zero Target</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p><strong>Definition:</strong> A condition where carbon emissions released equal carbon removed from the atmosphere.</p>
        <div class="formula-box">
          <div class="formula-text">🏭 Carbon Emitted = 🌲 Carbon Removed → 🎯 Net Zero</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card light-u6"><span class="ic-icon">☀️</span><div class="ic-label">Renewable Energy</div><div class="ic-sub">Reduces emissions</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u6"><span class="ic-icon">🌲</span><div class="ic-label">Afforestation</div><div class="ic-sub">Increases carbon removal</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u6"><span class="ic-icon">🔬</span><div class="ic-label">Carbon Capture</div><div class="ic-sub">Tech to absorb CO₂</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#e8f8f5;border-color:var(--u6);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u6">🇮🇳 India's Target</div>
          <div class="mb-content">India aims to achieve Net Zero by <strong>2070</strong> 🎯</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u6">⚖️ 5. Climate Justice</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p><strong>Definition:</strong> The idea that climate change disproportionately affects poor and developing countries, even though they contribute less to pollution.</p>
        <div class="compare-row">
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#fdf2f2;border-left:4px solid var(--u4)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u4)">😢 Who Suffers More?</h4>
            <ul><li>Poor &amp; developing nations</li><li>Small island nations (sea rise)</li><li>Agricultural communities (drought)</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#eafaf1;border-left:4px solid var(--u1)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u1)">✅ Principle of Justice</h4>
            <ul><li>Big polluters must take greater responsibility</li><li>Developed nations provide climate finance</li><li>Technology transfer to developing nations</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u6">📊 6. Carbon Intensity vs Energy Intensity</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <table class="styled-table">
          <thead><tr><th class="bg-u6">Feature</th><th class="bg-u6">Carbon Intensity 🏭</th><th class="bg-u6">Energy Intensity ⚡</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Measures</td><td>CO₂ emitted per unit of output</td><td>Energy consumed per unit of output</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Indicates</td><td>Level of pollution</td><td>Level of efficiency</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Goal</td><td>Lower is better ✅</td><td>Lower is better ✅</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u6">📋 7. National Clean Air Programme (NCAP)</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Government initiative to reduce environmental and climate impacts especially air pollution in Indian cities.</p>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card light-u6"><span class="ic-icon">💨</span><div class="ic-label">Improve Air Quality</div><div class="ic-sub">Reduce PM2.5 &amp; PM10</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u6"><span class="ic-icon">🏙️</span><div class="ic-label">Target Cities</div><div class="ic-sub">122 non-attainment cities</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u6"><span class="ic-icon">💚</span><div class="ic-label">Health Benefit</div><div class="ic-sub">Cleaner air = better health</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="qr-strip">
      <h4>⚡ Unit 6 Quick Revision</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>🌡️ Global Warming → Temperature Rise due to GHGs</li>
        <li>🌀 Climate Change → Long-term weather pattern changes</li>
        <li>🌲 Carbon Sink → Forests, Oceans, Wetlands absorb CO₂</li>
        <li>🎯 Net Zero → Emission = Removal (India target: 2070)</li>
        <li>⚖️ Climate Justice → Poor nations suffer more, rich nations responsible</li>
        <li>📊 Carbon Intensity → CO₂ per output | Energy Intensity → Energy per output</li>
        <li>📋 NCAP → Reduce air pollution in Indian cities</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ─── IMP UNIT 7 ─── -->
<div class="imp-unit-card">
  <div class="imp-unit-header bg-u7" onclick="toggleImp(this)">
    <span class="imp-unit-badge">UNIT 7</span>
    <span style="font-size:1.5rem">⚙️</span>
    <h3>Environmental Management Master Notes — Articles, ISO 14001, LCA, Circular Economy, EIA</h3>
    <button class="toggle-btn">▼</button>
  </div>
  <div class="imp-unit-body">

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u7">📜 1. Article 48A vs Article 51A(g)</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="compare-row">
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#fef5e7;border-left:4px solid var(--u7)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u7)">🏛️ Article 48A — Government Duty</h4>
            <p style="font-size:.85rem;margin-bottom:8px"><strong>Directive Principles of State Policy</strong></p>
            <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted);">"The State shall protect and improve the environment and safeguard forests and wildlife."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="compare-card" style="background:#eafaf1;border-left:4px solid var(--u1)">
            <h4 style="color:var(--u1)">👤 Article 51A(g) — Citizen Duty</h4>
            <p style="font-size:.85rem;margin-bottom:8px"><strong>Fundamental Duties of Citizens</strong></p>
            <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted);">Every citizen must protect forests, lakes, rivers, and wildlife.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#fef5e7;border-color:var(--u7)">
          <div class="mb-title text-u7">🧠 Memory Trick</div>
          <div class="mb-content">48A → Government Protects 🏛️ &nbsp;|&nbsp; 51A(g) → Citizen Protects 👤</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u7">🏅 2. ISO 14001 — Environmental Management System</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>International standard for Environmental Management Systems (EMS). Helps organizations improve environmental performance.</p>
        <div class="imp-flow">
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u2">📋 Plan — Set objectives</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u1">✅ Do — Implement actions</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u5">🔍 Check — Monitor &amp; measure</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u7">🔄 Act — Review &amp; improve</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u6">📈 Continuous Improvement</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tag-list" style="margin-top:10px">
          <span class="tag bg-u7">♻️ Reduce Pollution</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u7">📊 Better Performance</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u7">⚖️ Legal Compliance</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u7">🏆 Better Image</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u7">🔬 3. Life Cycle Analysis (LCA)</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p><strong>Definition:</strong> Study of environmental impact of a product from birth to death (cradle to grave).</p>
        <div class="imp-flow">
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#3498db">⛏️ Raw Material Extraction</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node" style="background:#e67e22">🏭 Manufacturing</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u1">🛒 Use by Consumer</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u4">🗑️ Disposal / End of Life</div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#fef5e7;border-color:var(--u7);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u7">🧠 Example</div>
          <div class="mb-content">Plastic bottle: Extract oil → Manufacture → Use → Thrown away → Pollutes land</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u7">🔄 4. Circular Economy</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p><strong>Definition:</strong> Economic system where resources are reused repeatedly to minimize waste generation.</p>
        <div class="imp-flow">
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u1">🏭 Produce</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u2">🛒 Use</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u5">🔁 Reuse</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u6">♻️ Recycle</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u1">🏭 Produce Again ↺</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tag-list" style="margin-top:10px">
          <span class="tag bg-u7">📉 Less Waste</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u7">♻️ Resource Conservation</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u7">🌱 Sustainable Development</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u7">♻️ 5. 3R Concept — Reduce, Reuse, Recycle</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="effect-row">
          <div class="effect-card light-u1"><span class="ec-icon">📉</span><div class="ec-title text-u1">REDUCE</div><ul><li>Use fewer resources</li><li>Example: Use digital notes instead of paper ✅</li></ul></div>
          <div class="effect-card light-u2"><span class="ec-icon">🔁</span><div class="ec-title text-u2">REUSE</div><ul><li>Use items multiple times</li><li>Example: Reuse water bottles ✅</li></ul></div>
          <div class="effect-card light-u6"><span class="ec-icon">♻️</span><div class="ec-title text-u6">RECYCLE</div><ul><li>Convert waste into new products</li><li>Example: Recycling paper into notebooks ✅</li></ul></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u7">📋 6. Environmental Impact Assessment (EIA)</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p><strong>Definition:</strong> Process to evaluate environmental effects before starting any major project.</p>
        <div class="imp-flow">
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u2">📝 Project Proposal</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u6">🔬 Environmental Study</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u5">📊 Impact Assessment</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u3">📣 Public Consultation</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u7">📄 Final Report</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:16px">
            <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u1">✅ Approval</div>
            <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u4">❌ Rejection</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#fef5e7;border-color:var(--u7);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u7">🧠 Example</div>
          <div class="mb-content">Before building a dam → EIA studies impact on rivers, forests, wildlife, and nearby villages.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="qr-strip">
      <h4>⚡ Unit 7 Quick Revision</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>🏛️ Article 48A → Government must protect environment</li>
        <li>👤 Article 51A(g) → Citizens must protect environment</li>
        <li>🏅 ISO 14001 → Plan → Do → Check → Act (EMS Standard)</li>
        <li>🔬 LCA → Study product impact from Raw Material to Disposal</li>
        <li>🔄 Circular Economy → Produce → Use → Reuse → Recycle → Repeat</li>
        <li>♻️ 3R → Reduce + Reuse + Recycle</li>
        <li>📋 EIA → Environmental study before any major project</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ─── IMP UNIT 8 ─── -->
<div class="imp-unit-card">
  <div class="imp-unit-header bg-u8" onclick="toggleImp(this)">
    <span class="imp-unit-badge">UNIT 8</span>
    <span style="font-size:1.5rem">📜</span>
    <h3>Treaties Master Notes — Montreal, Kyoto, Paris, CBD, COP, IPCC, IUCN &amp; Indian Laws</h3>
    <button class="toggle-btn">▼</button>
  </div>
  <div class="imp-unit-body">

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u8">🌀 1. Montreal Protocol (1987)</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="effect-row">
          <div class="effect-card light-u8"><span class="ec-icon">🎯</span><div class="ec-title text-u8">Purpose</div><ul><li>Protection of ozone layer</li><li>Phase out CFC production &amp; use</li></ul></div>
          <div class="effect-card light-u1"><span class="ec-icon">✅</span><div class="ec-title text-u1">Success Story</div><ul><li>Ozone layer is gradually recovering</li><li>Most successful environmental treaty</li></ul></div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#eaf2fb;border-color:var(--u8);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u8">🧠 Memory</div>
          <div class="mb-content">Montreal (1987) = 🌀 Ozone Protection — Most Successful Treaty!</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u8">🏭 2. Kyoto Protocol (1997)</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>First international treaty with <strong>legally binding</strong> greenhouse gas emission reduction targets — primarily for developed nations.</p>
        <div class="tag-list">
          <span class="tag bg-u8">📉 Reduce GHG Emissions</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u8">⚖️ Legally Binding</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u8">🌍 Developed Nations Focus</span>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#eaf2fb;border-color:var(--u8);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u8">🧠 Memory</div>
          <div class="mb-content">Kyoto (1997) = 🏭 Cut Emissions — First Legally Binding Climate Treaty</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u8">🌍 3. Paris Agreement (2015)</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Landmark global agreement — all nations (developed and developing) committed to climate action. Came from <strong>COP21</strong>.</p>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card light-u8"><span class="ic-icon">🌡️</span><div class="ic-label">Goal</div><div class="ic-sub">Limit warming to 1.5–2°C above pre-industrial levels</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u8"><span class="ic-icon">🌍</span><div class="ic-label">Participation</div><div class="ic-sub">All nations included (195 countries)</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u8"><span class="ic-icon">📋</span><div class="ic-label">NDCs</div><div class="ic-sub">Each country submits National Action Plans</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#eaf2fb;border-color:var(--u8);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u8">🧠 Memory</div>
          <div class="mb-content">Paris (2015) = 🌍 Climate Action for ALL Nations — Limit 1.5°C!</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u8">🌿 4. Convention on Biological Diversity (CBD) — 1992</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Started at the <strong>Rio Earth Summit 1992.</strong> Three core objectives:</p>
        <div class="imp-flow">
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u1">🛡️ Conservation of Biodiversity</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u6">♻️ Sustainable Use of Resources</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u5">🤝 Fair Sharing of Benefits</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u8">🌊 5. Ramsar Convention (1971)</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>International treaty for conservation and sustainable use of wetlands.</p>
        <div class="tag-list">
          <span class="tag bg-u8">🌊 Lakes</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u8">🌿 Marshes</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u8">🌴 Mangroves</span>
          <span class="tag bg-u8">🌾 Peatlands</span>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#eaf2fb;border-color:var(--u8);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u8">🧠 Memory</div>
          <div class="mb-content">Ramsar (1971) = 🌊 Wetlands Protection</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u8">🌐 6. Conference of Parties (COP)</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Annual meeting of all countries under the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC).</p>
        <div class="imp-flow">
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u8">🌍 Countries Meet (Annually)</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u2">💬 Discuss Climate Issues &amp; Progress</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="imp-flow-node bg-u1">📜 Make Global Agreements</div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#eaf2fb;border-color:var(--u8);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u8">🧠 Key Example</div>
          <div class="mb-content">COP21 (Paris 2015) → Paris Agreement | COP26 (Glasgow 2021) → Net Zero commitments</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u8">🔬 7. IPCC — Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card light-u8"><span class="ic-icon">📅</span><div class="ic-label">Established</div><div class="ic-sub">1988 by UNEP &amp; WMO</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u8"><span class="ic-icon">📊</span><div class="ic-label">Function</div><div class="ic-sub">Assess climate research &amp; publish reports</div></div>
          <div class="info-card light-u8"><span class="ic-icon">🏛️</span><div class="ic-label">Importance</div><div class="ic-sub">Scientific basis for climate policies worldwide</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-box" style="background:#eaf2fb;border-color:var(--u8);margin-top:10px">
          <div class="mb-title text-u8">🧠 Memory</div>
          <div class="mb-content">IPCC = 🔬 Climate Scientists of the World — They say what the science shows!</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u8">🦁 8. IUCN — International Union for Conservation of Nature</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <p>Prepares the <strong>Red List</strong> — the world's most comprehensive inventory of threatened species.</p>
        <div class="iucn-ladder">
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#2ecc71;width:320px">✅ LC — Least Concern</div>
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#f1c40f;color:#333;width:280px;margin-top:4px">⚠️ NT — Near Threatened</div>
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#e67e22;width:240px;margin-top:4px">🔶 VU — Vulnerable</div>
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#e74c3c;width:200px;margin-top:4px">🔴 EN — Endangered (e.g. Tiger 🐯)</div>
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#c0392b;width:160px;margin-top:4px">🆘 CR — Critically Endangered</div>
          <div class="iucn-rung" style="background:#7f8c8d;width:120px;margin-top:4px">💀 EX — Extinct (e.g. Dodo)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imp-topic">
      <div class="imp-topic-head bg-u8">🇮🇳 9. Key Environmental Laws of India</div>
      <div class="imp-topic-body">
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-dot bg-u1">72</div>
            <div class="tl-year text-u1">1972</div>
            <div class="tl-content border-u1"><h4>📗 Wildlife Protection Act</h4><p>Protects wild animals and plants. Created National Parks and Wildlife Sanctuaries.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-dot bg-u2">74</div>
            <div class="tl-year text-u2">1974</div>
            <div class="tl-content border-u2"><h4>💧 Water (Prevention &amp; Control of Pollution) Act</h4><p>Prevents and controls water pollution from industries and sewage.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-dot bg-u4">81</div>
            <div class="tl-year text-u4">1981</div>
            <div class="tl-content border-u4"><h4>💨 Air (Prevention &amp; Control of Pollution) Act</h4><p>Controls air pollution and sets standards for emissions.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-dot bg-u7">86</div>
            <div class="tl-year text-u7">1986</div>
            <div class="tl-content border-u7"><h4>🌍 Environment Protection Act</h4><p>Umbrella legislation — empowers government to take all measures for environmental protection.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="qr-strip">
      <h4>⚡ Unit 8 Quick Revision</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>🌀 Montreal (1987) → Ozone Layer Protection</li>
        <li>🏭 Kyoto (1997) → GHG Emission Reduction (Legally Binding)</li>
        <li>🌍 Paris (2015) → Climate Action for ALL — Limit 1.5–2°C</li>
        <li>🌿 CBD (1992) → Conserve + Sustainable Use + Share Benefits</li>
        <li>🌊 Ramsar (1971) → Wetlands Protection</li>
        <li>🦁 CITES (1973) → Stop Illegal Wildlife Trade</li>
        <li>🌐 COP → Annual climate meetings (COP21 = Paris Agreement)</li>
        <li>🔬 IPCC (1988) → Climate Science Body</li>
        <li>🦁 IUCN → Red List: EX → CR → EN → VU → NT → LC</li>
        <li>🇮🇳 India: Wildlife Act 1972 | Water Act 1974 | Air Act 1981 | EPA 1986</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

